Sync Input Data to Remote

dpinput_sync.Rd

Sync input data for a data product build to a remote like a labkey or AWS S3

dpinput_sync(conf, input_map, verbose = F, ...)

Arguments

conf

environment containing all config.R variables. See dpconf_get()
input_map

object containing all input data to be synced. See map_input()
verbose

T/F
...

other parameters e.g. verbose = T

Value

synced_map this is input_map with sync status added to metadata
